<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ عُبَادَةُ:</span> بَايَعْنَا النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> أَنْ لَا نَنْتَهِبَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>